{"tid":2457342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沒吃渣 這剎那被破壞嗎","createTime":"2021-03-22T14:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T05:18:59.000Z","uid":343520,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f2318863522fb96dc16f3ec6aa37dfa61be8dbf7","tid":2457342,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"沒吃渣 這剎那被破壞嗎<br />\n銅記的分店收檔喇<br />\n肥燶叉加錢變左湯渣<br />\n<br />\n你說我未能定時<br />\n自費每天幫襯一次<br />\n俊傑說出一句美麗台詞<br />\n大眾捐出資金當做善事<br />\n「求下你再信我一次」<br />\n<br />\n牛肉不熟亦並沒罪名<br />\n全憑煮不熟的口感取勝<br />\n從來就察覺你每個動作<br />\n是買通多少打手的鐵證<br />\n<br />\n龍門叉蛋飯盛惠六十元<br />\n然而不好食亦並沒事情<br />\n全憑藉老細嘅語氣動聽<br />\n在佢facebook中多次說明<br />\n撐手足要用幫襯 保證<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞在 ※ <a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=2c829a73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">passiontimes.hk/</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tYGxOB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tYGxOB.jpg&h=c886a7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwebaB3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwebaB3.jpg&h=33c5fc33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7owQraM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7owQraM.png&h=2d652038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e2daa4fe2a43f550509b49ca79b39e4c250c624","tid":2457342,"uid":372210,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc14d0f01cb6676b522d25aca27090999d78fcf8","tid":2457342,"uid":154406,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset